command_group: az network front-door waf-policy managed-rules override
description: View and alter overrides on managed rules within a managed rule set.

commands.name: az network front-door waf-policy managed-rules override add
commands.summary: Add an override on a managed rule within a managed rule set.
commands.syntax:
az network front-door waf-policy managed-rules override add --rule-group-id
                                                            --rule-id
                                                            --type
                                                            [--action {Allow, AnomalyScoring, Block, JSChallenge, Log, Redirect}]
                                                            [--disabled {false, true}]
                                                            [--ids]
                                                            [--policy-name]
                                                            [--resource-group]
                                                            [--subscription]

commands.name: az network front-door waf-policy managed-rules override list
commands.summary: List the overrides on managed rules within a managed rule set.
commands.syntax:
az network front-door waf-policy managed-rules override list --policy-name
                                                             --resource-group
                                                             --type

commands.name: az network front-door waf-policy managed-rules override remove
commands.summary: Remove an override on a managed rule within a managed rule set.
commands.syntax:
az network front-door waf-policy managed-rules override remove --rule-group-id
                                                               --rule-id
                                                               --type
                                                               [--ids]
                                                               [--policy-name]
                                                               [--resource-group]
                                                               [--subscription]
